OL,6,FA 34-year-old woman who died after
OL,7,Fbeing hit by a double-decker bus in
OL,8,FNottingham city centre has been named
OL,9,Fas Helaleh Cheraghmakani.
OL,11,FHelaleh died from her injuries after
OL,12,Fshe was hit by a Nottingham City
OL,13,FTransport bus in Lower Parliament
OL,14,FStreet on the morning of Tuesday,
OL,15,FOctober 22.
OL,17,FIn a tribute, she was described by her
OL,18,Ffamily as a 'devoted wife and a loving
OL,19,Fmother'. In a statement, her family
OL,20,Fsaid: "Helaleh was a rare soul ` the
OL,21,Fmost genuine person you could meet.
