OL,6,F"She was a devoted wife and a loving
OL,7,Fmother and, at just 34, she was old
OL,8,Fenough to carry lifelong dreams and
OL,9,Fhopes. Heartbreakingly, she was taken
OL,10,Ffrom us too soon. Helaleh faced life's
OL,11,Fchallenges with courage ` always
OL,12,Fputting others before herself. Her
OL,13,Fstrength and responsibility inspired
OL,14,Feveryone who knew her.
