OL,6,F"She had a way of caring deeply for
OL,7,Feveryone she met, bringing warmth and
OL,8,Fkindness into every room. Her innocent
OL,9,Fdeparture leaves a profound emptiness
OL,10,Fin our lives, but her memory will live
OL,11,Fon in the love she gave and the lives
OL,12,Fshe touched.
OL,14,F"We will always remember her for the
OL,15,Fjoy she brought and the unwavering
OL,16,Fcompassion that defined her life."
OL,18,FThe 34-year-old was treated by the
OL,19,Femergency services at the scene but
OL,20,Fdied a short time later.
