OL,6,FAn online fundraising page has also
OL,7,Fbeen set up to support Helaleh's
OL,8,Ffamily in the wake of her passing, and
OL,9,Fhas already raised #13,000.
OL,11,FThe GoFundMe page, established by
OL,12,Ffriend Elaheh Arjmand, carries a
OL,13,Fstatement which says: "She touched the
OL,14,Flives of everyone she met with her
OL,15,Fwarmth, kindness, and strength. Her
OL,16,Fpassing has left all of us
OL,17,Fheartbroken, especially her husband
OL,18,FRamin who must now struggle to
OL,19,Fnavigate this unimaginable loss.
